      "text": "それで……{user}さんになら\n相談出来るかもって……",
      "startTime": 67.8673592886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.36735878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この間、俺が言ったことをちゃんと覚えてて\nくれて嬉しいよ。電話してくれてありがとう",
      "startTime": 72.5333456676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
